<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Swifty Care</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-image: url('https://your-image-link.com/header-background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            background-image: url('https://your-image-link.com/content-background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .content h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 22px;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .groceries-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .grocery-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .grocery-item img {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 300px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            Welcome to Swifty Care!
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
            <p>Thank you for joining Swifty Care. We are excited to have you on board.</p>
            <p>We strive to provide the best service possible, and we're here to assist you with any needs or questions you may have.</p>
            <p><strong>Your Registered Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
            <p><strong>Your Suggestions:</strong> <%= suggestions %></p>

            <!-- App Image Section -->
            <div class="groceries-section">
                <h3>Our App at a Glance</h3>
                <div class="grocery-item">
                    <img src="https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/05/89/90/83/360_F_589908398_6RaggcvYGDzFF0Oh2JAcepJHeU6XLJEZ.jpg" alt="Swifty Care App">
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any additional questions, feel free to reply to this email or visit our <a href="https://swyftclient.onrender.com/contact">contact page</a> for more ways to reach out.</p>
            <p>We look forward to supporting you on your journey with us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Swifty Care &copy; 2024</p>
            <p>
                <a href="https://swyft-project.onrender.com">Visit our website</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:swiftycare92@gmail.com">Contact Support</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>